This project ("ZONOS2-mlx") is an independent Apple Silicon / MLX inference
reimplementation. It loads the open-weight ZONOS2 checkpoint published by
Zyphra (https://huggingface.co/Zyphra/ZONOS2) but does not redistribute the
model weights. ZONOS2, the descript-audio-codec vocoder, the speaker encoder
and MLX are the property of their respective authors and remain under their
own licenses.

